This #GivingTuesday I am providing my support for the next generation of cyclists, for unrestricted access to bicycles worldwide, and for opportunities for all individuals to harness the power of cycling. I support @outride and their mission to use cycling to improve social, emotional, and cognitive health. Outride allows me to donate through the link in my bio or the “Donate” button on their Facebook. 
Give a kid two wheels and you give them the world. Let’s see how far their legs can take them. So, what will you Outride?
#whatwillyououtride #givingtuesday #ridingforfocus #morekidsonbikes

Congratulations to @andrea__snowflake, @dive_2_live, @sylwia.slotwinska, @yungfayjai and @simone_po93 for being the five winners of the Black Friday giveaway! You will each be contacted by DM in order to get your cool shades! #ride100percent

Pomôžme teraz my slovenskej polícii! S českými kolegami súperia o počet followerov. Víťaz získa podporu pre charitu, naši hrajú pre detských onkologických pacientov. Čechov je raz tak ako nás, preto naši potrebujú každého nového fanúšika! Sledujte ich na @policiaslovakia už teraz! Deadline je už v sobotu o polnoci.

Hello everybody, the Slovak police need your help! They are competing with their Czech colleagues in the number of followers for a very worthy cause! If they win, they will receive support to help sick children. It's a tight competition, so every single follower counts. The deadline is on Saturday midnight, so please follow them right now on @policiaslovakia!

Who wants the gift of 100% during this holiday season? I'm giving away 5 pairs of 100% sunglasses on Black Friday and you could win a fresh pair of eyewear like the Renshaw I'm wearing. All you have to do is follow @ride100percent, choose any model of 100% sunglasses you like and tell us which one it is! Five winners will be randomly chosen and each will receive the model they like! @100percent_vision #ride100percent #see100percent #blackfriday
It was such a pleasure riding in Barranquilla at the @saganfondocolombia with all my friends and fans from Colombia, Latin America and beyond! Muchas gracias a todos and I hope to see you again soon!

Thanks to the 2,000 participants at the @saganfondocolombia for making it such a huge success! It was a great pleasure spending three days in Barranquilla and I can't wait to be back in Colombia, a country that loves cycling!

Great Saturday ride in Barranquilla at the @saganfondocolombia!

Photos @pipecano_photo

In Barranquilla, surrounded by participants of the @saganfondocolombia! What a start to the weekend!

Gracias a todos!

I'm in Barranquilla right now, ready for the @saganfondocolombia, which promises to be an amazing event with thousands of participants, just like the @saganfondogranroadieoh in San Diego last week. It was a blast and we had so much fun, on and off our bikes! Check this video with some of the best images from the three-day bike festival and remember, cycling is fun! FULL video on Instagram TV!

I'd like to thank all the participants that had such a great time and everybody that worked and contributed to making it happen! @iamspecialized @ride100percent @sportful @osmonutrition @gopro @cafoundation
Last week, I visited the @iamspecialized headquarters in Morgan Hill, California and after a hard day's work, we had some fun in the wind tunnel...

What a day! It wasn't just a great ride together with all the participants of the first @saganfondogranroadieoh in San Diego, it was the culmination of a three-day festival with bikes that started on Friday. 
Enjoy these photos by @veloimages and during the next few days, you'll get to see more from this event that brings fun to cycling and supports worthy causes.

Once again, I'd like to thank everybody that supported us and worked hard to make this a success!

@iamspecialized @sportful @ride100percent @osmonutrition @cafoundation @outride

Fun ride today with Chris and Rebecca from Chicago. Thanks to their generosity we were able to contribute to the great work of @cafoundation and @outride. Can't wait to ride on Sunday morning with all the participants of the @saganfondogranroadieoh

Thanks to Chris and Rebecca from Chicago for their generosity in the Charity Auction of the @saganfondogranroadieoh. They get to ride with me today... @iamspecialized @ride100percent @sportful @osmonutrition @gopro @cafoundation @outride

Yesterday, I visited the @iamspecialized headquarters in Morgan Hill and I was intrigued by a green door with my name on it. I didn't know anything about it but a big surprise was hiding behind it. Thanks, Mike Sinyard, Mark Cote and everybody else at Specialized for building this fantastic "Sagan Room", it's an honor and privilege for me. I'm so happy to see it!
